author: Kuokka77
description:
"Just Married!", an Amiga cover of C64 Robocop theme by Jogeir Liljedahl. Original C64 theme by Jonathan Dunn (1988).
C64 art "Waiting for Christmas" (2022) by Mikael & The Sarge/Fairlight^Pretzel Logic.

Made using real A600 Rev. 2D audio.

Visit my channel for more Amiga music.
title: Amiga music: Jogeir Liljedahl - Just Married! (Robocop C64 theme cover) (A600r2d🎧Dolbyfied)
